snippet.title: Gameplay Footage of "Cthulhu Frozen Nightmare" by Virtua Worlds
snippet.description:
Gameplay Footage of "Cthulhu Frozen Nightmare" by Virtua Worlds for the Unreal Spring Jam 2020. Download for free at https://virtuaworlds.itch.io/cthulhu-frozen-nightmare
Music by Mercurius FM https://mercuriusfm.com/

This game was made in less than 5 days.
